VDS-CSS: VDS Coordinator and Workflow Manager for CSS
------------------------------------------------------

Dependencies
---------------
   - Tigres
   - MongoDB

Pre-requisites
---------------

Usage
---------------
1. Using the VDS API [to be used by programmers]
   - compose a data-centric workflow using VDS Coordinator
     -- add VDOs to a VDS
     -- add producers and consumers to VDOs
     -- create data tasks (if necessary)

2. Using a workflow description [to be used by direct users]
   - provide a description of the workflow (including data descriptions)
   - select the appropriate data management strategy
   - generate batch scripts through the code generator
   - submit the batch scripts through batch schedulers 

Test
----------------
1. start the data orchestrator
      python utils/data_orchestrator.py

2. monitor the task status
      python db/monitor.py

3. run the test
      python tests/test.py

-- the status of tasks should change from PENDING to COMPLETED as the test executes
   and the data orchestrator updates the data task status

